Package pacman.model

Class Map

  • java.lang.Object
    • pacman.model.Map
  • public class Map
extends java.lang.Object

    Map

    A Map is an object consisting of different types of Grid, a configuration object MapConfig and some setup configurations.

    Since:
    1.0
    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    Song Zhang
    See Also:
    Grid, MovableGrid, Cookie, Ghost, Obstacle, Pacman, Portal, Spawn, MapConfig, MapReader, MapPainter

      • read

        private void read()
        Reads the map file of fileName.

      • draw

        public void draw​(javafx.scene.layout.Pane root)
        Draws the map to the given Pane node.

        This method calls read() to get result first, then uses MapPainter to paint the map.

        Parameters:
        root - a Pane that is expected to be drawn with the map on it
